My suggestion is to make friends with a low level and buy the dusts from him for just over what a vendor would give him.  You can get stacks at a time for cheap.  Or have your Guild farm them for you with their low chars.  One way or another you're getting something for cheap or nothing.  I'm currenty working on my skill, it's at about 119, gonna try for 250 so I can make the GM Vial but I'm having my Guild and friends help me with the components.  It's crazy if you want to go out and get them yourselves.  <br>
